    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-08-19T17:55:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-08-17T23:16:00-05:00" n="24"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d24">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">
                        <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Acting
                            Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Buenos Aires</hi>
                        </placeName>[, <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1906-08-19T17:55:00-05:00"
                            notBefore="1906-08-18T00:00:00-04:16">undated</date>].<lb/>Received 5.55
                        p.m. August 19, 1906.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am leaving Buenos Aires this afternoon, after a most hospitable and friendly
                    reception and entertainment. Owing to the terrible calamity in Chile I have
                    advised Chilean Government that I will, with their permission, limit my visit to
                    a simple call of condolence. I have expressed sympathy in personal call at
                    Chilean legation here by telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Root.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
